quran[8{c,v,t}:
2,17,inn ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aikshakhs ne aag roshan ki aur jab uss ne saaray mahol ko roshan kar diya to Allah ne inn ka noor Basarat salb kar liya aur inhen is haal mein chore diya ke tarikeon mein inhen kuch nazar nahi aata
2,18,"yeh behray hain, gungay hain, andhay hain, yeh ab nah paltainge"
2,19,"ya phir un ki misaal yun samjhoo ke aasman se zor ki barish ho rahi hai aur is ke sath andheri ghata aur karrak chamak bhi hai, yeh bijli ke krhake sun kar apni jaanun ke khauf se kaanon mein ungelianthons letay hain aur Allah innmunkareen haq ko har taraf se ghairay mein liye hue hai"
2,20,"chamak se un ki haalat yeh ho rahi hai ke goya anqareeb bijli inn ki Basarat uchak le jaye gi jab zara kuch roshni inhen mehsoos hoti hai to iss mein kuch daur chal letay hain aur jab un par andhera chhaa jata hai to khar y ho jatay hain Allah chahta to un ki samaat aur Basarat bilkul hi salb kar laita, yaqeenan woh har cheez par Qadir hai"
2,21,"logo! bandagi ikhtiyar karo apne uss Rab ki jo tumhara aur tum se pehlay jo log ho guzray hain unn sab ka khaaliq hai, tumahray bachney ki tawaqqa isi soorat hosakti hai"
2,22,"wohi to hai jiss ne tumahray liye zameen ka farsh bichhaya, aasman ki chhat banai, oopar se pani barsaya aur is ke zariye se har terhan ki pedawar nikaal kar tumahray liye rizaq baham pohanchaya pas jab tum yeh jantay ho to dosaron ko Allah ka maday muqabil nah therao"
2,23,"aur agar tumhe iss amar mein shak hai ke yeh kittab jo hum ne apne bande par utari hai, yeh hamari hai ya nahi, tu is ke manind aik hi sourat bana lao, apne saaray humnawaoan ko bulaa lau, aik Allah ko chore kar baqi jis jis ki chaho, madad le lau, agar tum sachey ho"
2,24,"to yeh kaam kar ke dikhao, lekin agar tum ne aisa nah kya aur yaqeenan kabhi nahi kar saktay, to daro is aag se jis ka eendhan banain ge ensaan aur pathar, jo muhayya ki gayi hai munkareen haq ke liye"
